data.description: Discover the potential at 1709 2nd Street NE, an exciting opportunity nestled in the heart of Winter Haven. This residence featuring 3 bedrooms and 1.5 baths is a hidden gem awaiting your creative touch to become your dream home or a valuable addition to your investment portfolio.  Step inside, and you'll find three spacious and functional bedrooms. The kitchen seamlessly connects to a spacious living area, providing the perfect backdrop for unfolding your design vision. With 1114 SqFt of space, the potential for customization is endless.  It is situated on a DOUBLE LOT, spanning .23 acre, providing plenty of room and endless outdoor possibilities.    This property is in a prime location, offering both convenience and potential. The home is being sold in AS IS condition, making it an excellent candidate for transformation. Whether you're looking for a place to call home or seeking a great investment opportunity this property delivers. Your vision awaits – make it a reality today!
